title: Bloomberg Markets: Fischer to Step Down in Mid-October
itunes:title: Bloomberg Markets: Fischer to Step Down in Mid-October
description:
Bloomberg Markets with Carol Massar and Cory Johnson. GUEST: Craig Torres Federal Reserve Reporter Bloomberg News Discussing Federal Reserve Vice Chairman Stanley Fischer announcing he has resigned effective on or around Oct. 13 after serving three years at the U.S. central bank.
